                "en": "Every sunday morning I commit myself to entertain more than 30 kids. But there is more to being a leader than just that. I also help with the organisation of camps, hikes and other activities. Also communicating with parents is an important responsibility. Being a leader has taught me a lot about teamwork, responsibility and communication."
